      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORF (2) has disappointed in two runs back this time, but now lines up for the Peter Fernie barn with a tongue tie on. The inside draw is a big tick and Fiore's booking is a positive sign. Maps to get his chance back in trip slightly and he can make a statement. DANCEWITHME (1) tackled a strong form race two back before a 1.9L defeat at this track and trip last time out. Faithfull hops on board today in a good push for her chances as she lines up here on the quick turnaround. Loves this track and trip and can make her presence felt. QUEEN SELYSE (3) made it back-to-back wins last start with a 0.2L victory over 1200m last week. On the quick turnaround today and back to 1100m, but she's in winning form and can keep the ball rolling. COULDABEENAHANDBAG (7) wasn't far off last start at this track and trip and has claims. FAVOURITE SONGS (5) won't be far away.",
